  "title": "Pirkei Avot §avot_04_04: Rabbi Levitas a man of Yavneh said: be exceeding humble spirit, for the end o...",
  "body": "Rabbi Levitas a man of Yavneh said: be exceeding humble spirit, for the end of man is the worm. Rabbi Yohanan ben Berokah said: whoever profanes the name of heaven in secret, he shall be punished in the open. Unwittingly or wittingly, it is all one in profaning the name.",
